game.name: Baby Elsa Halloween Surgery
game.description:
Baby Elsa loves playing outside with her friends. She is also a big lover of candies and keeps asking for candies. Today she has come in front of a house and shouted asking for the candies for long, but nobody came to respond her. She has fallen down while returning from there. Now she needs a doctor who will take care of her injury and help her to recover fast. Would you like this free online html5 game as a doctor? Join Baby Elsa Halloween Surgery game and be prepared to provide this little girl with the needful first aid!
Apart from helping her to recover from her sudden injury, you also have to help the girl to choose a perfect outfit for the tonight Halloween party. Clean her injury with the liquid, remove the thorn with the tool, and give her the needful plaster and use the patch to get her injury cured fast! Once you are done, click the right button and be prepared to help the little baby to choose a nice spooky Halloween dress. Change her hairstyle, and an elegant top and a suitable bottom! 
Make sure to combine her dress with a pair of lovely sandals or shoes. Try to complete both the tasks as fast as you can and help this little girl to feel better than ever in this brand new doctor game! We are sure that your nice fashion sense will guide her to choose a perfect dress for the occasion and make her feel proud on your choice. We are delighted to carry a wider range of new html5 princess dress up games that are free to play online, no download required.
